sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor U as User
    participant V as Viewer Count Service
    participant R as Redis
    participant K as Kafka

    Note over U,K: 1. Heartbeat
    loop every 30s
        U->>V: user still watching
        V->>K: publish ViewerHeartbeat {streamId, userId}
        K->>V: consume ViewerHeartbeat
        V->>R: SETEX stream:{streamId}:viewer:{userId} 60
    end

    Note over V,R: 2. Ghost User Detection
    R->>V: EXPIRED stream:{streamId}:viewer:{userId}
    V->>R: SISMEMBER stream:{streamId}:viewers {userId}
    R-->>V: 1 or 0
    alt exists
        V->>R: SREM stream:{streamId}:viewers {userId}
        V->>R: DECR stream:{streamId}:viewer_count
    else already removed
    end